\begin_inset Formula $c\approx-z^{-1}$
\end_inset

 within the volume 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{0}$
\end_inset

, by way of the convolution relation and using a short hand notation 
\begin_inset Formula $z=\rho\kappa/\beta$
\end_inset

