\begin_inset Formula $\bar{n}_{\text{u}}^{(0)}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{\text{u}}^{(0)}$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{\text{u}}^{(1)}$
\end_inset

, used to describe the solute charge distribution 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{\text{u}}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

